title: SNIPER BLACKLIST-PLAZA
description:
ABOUT THE GAME :

Make your way behind enemy lines in different environments like desert,jungle and island.
You are a sniper : Use your anemometer to know the wind speed, control your breath and apply windage and elevation corrections in your scope depending the distance.


Title: SNIPER BLACKLIST
Genre: Action, Adventure, Indie
Developer: jago138
Publisher: jago138
Release Date: 11 Aug, 2016

Minimum:
OS: windows 7 64 bit or later
Processor: intel core i5
Memory: 8 GB RAM
Graphics: nvidia 750 or equivalent
Storage: 18000 MB available space

Recommended:
OS: windows 7 64 bit or later
Processor: intel core i5
Memory: 8 GB RAM
Graphics: nvidia gtx 970 or equivalent
Storage: 18000 MB available space

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
5. Play!
